title: Soe Pyi Swar Vegetarian Centre
description: 斋全素食餐室 simple vegetarian cafe in Chinatown. Has an English menu. Offers many faux meats, which are typically served on a bed of vegetables. You could order off the menu as well or ask for mixed vegetable with or without tofu and a side of rice. The plates are large servings meant to be shared. 2014 relocated from 136 Latha St.
